data.title: Privilege Ibiza
data.meta_description: For all your Black Hole Recordings music, Black Hole Recordings merchandise and other Black Hole Recordings goodies. Magik Muzik Shop, the worldwide online dance music and merchandise store
data.text:
The biggest club in the world, Privilege Ibiza, and Black Hole Recordings present a fabulous double mixcompilation delivered by Java and Ned Shepard.Situated on Ibiza between Ibiza Town and San Antonio, you will find Privilege. Aptly named the world’s biggest club, Privilege has become the most outstanding and influential club on the island that delivers a unique and breath taking experience; a must visit for all Ibiza visitors and party people.

With world famous resident DJs such as Tiësto, Robbie Rivera and parties like SuperMartXé, Privilege will host thousands of guests during the summer of 2010; visitors who will all be a part of that once in a lifetime moment only to be found on Ibiza. To fully capture the extraordinary concept of the famous Ibiza venue, Black Hole Recordings and Privilege decided to join forces for the release of a double mix compilation that would perfectly represent the music and atmosphere of the club.

Disc 1 features a deep house mix by Java. Java was born in Ibiza and started his professional career as a dj in 1996. He started of at the famous club Pacha in Ibiza alongside DJ Pippi. At the same period he also started to play in the super club Space until 1998. With his deep house, electro and minimal style, Java has slowly built up a huge fan base, especially through the summer playing at Space. The result of that made him win the DJ Award 2001 as "Best Ibiza DJ". In 2002, Java wanted to look to the future and left his residency at Pacha due to more demand for gigs around the world, playing algongside some of clubland's finests DJs. From 2006 to 2008, Java has also been resident for one of Ibiza's most succesful club nights , "Home of La Troya", with DJ Oliver and Javi Muñoz. Java is also a well know producer and is signed as an artist for Vendetta Records (Spain) where he now also works as A&R for the label. He has also collaborated with other producers for Milk & Sugar Records (Germany), Joia Records, etc. Enjoy this deep house electro mix from Java en feel the Ibiza summer.

Disc 2 contains a vocal house mix by Ned Shepard. Ned Shepard, a household name in the industry from Montreal Canada, built his rep through his passion for music and started playing piano when he was 5 years old. His deep passion for crafting nice songs, drove him to the top as a multi-talented DJ/producer. He made songs for the labels Vandit, Bedrock, Yoshitoshi Records and Global Underground to name a few. In 2008 he thought it was time to start his own independent label called Harem Records together with Sultan. Ned and Sultan have turned out a string of successful singles including a cover of Olivia Newton John’s #1 hit “Let’s Get Physical,” “Block Party”and the vocal anthem“Jeopardy”. Whether it’s behind the decks, in the studio or at a keyboard, Ned is always dedicated to delivering quality music to fans and clubbers around the world. Have a listen to his high quality Ibiza Privilege release and get ready to be surprised.
